about.summary: doc to argparse driven by docopt

name: argopt
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "argopt" %}
{% set version = "0.6.1" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: c8ca9cdeb6bf5e8d6b0fb6a6cd3c676210fd3ebacdabab57f5b95d1ed514f0af

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 1
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - argopt

about:
  home: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/tqdm
  license: "MPL-2.0"
  license_family: MOZILLA
  summary: doc to argparse driven by docopt
  license_file: LICENCE
  dev_url: https://github.com/casperdcl/argopt
  doc_url: https://github.com/casperdcl/argopt

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - casperdcl
    - jiangweiyao
